  "title": "Class 4 Driver",
  "description": "<p>We are a ship chandler company looking for a responsible <strong>Class 4 Driver</strong> to join our team.</p>\n<p>successful candidate will be responsible for transporting goods or materials, ensuring timely delivery, and adhering to all safety and regulatory standards.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate heavy vehicles (Class 4 license required)</li>\n  <li>Loading goods onto the truck, ensuring safe transportation and proper handling</li>\n  <li>Collection of goods and empty bins from the terminal</li>\n  <li>Perform vehicle inspections before and after trips, ensuring vehicles are in good working condition</li>\n  <li>Adhere to traffic laws and regulations to ensure the safety of all road users</li>\n  <li>Maintain delivery records</li>\n  <li>Assist with other jobs as and when required</li>\n  <li>Salary: Basic $2800 - $3300 + Incentives</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Valid Class 4 driving license</strong></li>\n  <li>Proven experience as a heavy vehicle driver, preferably in a similar role</li>\n  <li>Ability to perform basic vehicle maintenance</li>\n  <li>Good time management skills</li>\n  <li>Physically fit to handle loading/unloading of goods</li>\n</ul>",
