    "uen": "199305221C",
    "description": "<p>SEVEN SEAS MARITIME SERVICES (SINGAPORE) PTE. LTD. is a world-leading ship supplier providing a wide array of products and services to the international shipping trade. In Singapore, Seven Seas’s 11,916 sqm facilities located in Tuas showcase the latest cold storage/freezer warehousing and together with our in-port warehouse in Tanjung Pelepas both ensure our customer orientated quality service throughout the Far East.</p>\n<p>Seven Seas provides 24/7 one stop service for ship supplies for containerships, bulk carriers, tankers, general cargo vessels as well as cruise liners. Our adminstrative workforce works 5.5 days and our operations teams are on 24hours standby 365 days.</p>\n<p>Today Seven Seas is one of Singapore’s leading suppliers to the shipping and offshore industries and is ISO 9001, ISO 14001, OHSAS 18001 and ISO 22000 certified.</p>",
